Description:
‘Back’ button of browser will not function if clicked by user. Only back button 
given on customer journey pages will take back to previous page.

Navigation Flow on Back Button
The application will navigate the user to ‘CNIC Input’ page on clicking 
the ‘Back’ button on the ‘Set Passcode’.
The application will not do any action on clicking back button on 
‘Product offering’ and ‘CNIC Input’ page.
